## 🛡️ Security Hardening Applied Throughout:

All Docker Compose configurations include security_opt flags as per v1.2 upgrade docs Section 4:
```yaml
security_opt: 
    - no-new-privileges:true     
      - apparmor=unconfined        # Enterprise tier ready
      
cap_drop:    
  - ALL                         # Drop all capabilities; add back selectively  

user_namespace_isolation_enabled = true (UID:${GID} mapping)  
```

